The paper is about online machine learning algorithms, which are commonly used in various fields such as artificial intelligence, data science, and computer vision. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the categorization of different algorithms and techniques, which falls under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Additionally, the paper briefly covers unsupervised online learning, which is related to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
